				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				As far as I know the Erudite Madman is a rare spawn.<BR>
I had been hunting Zombie sailors, wisps etc. on the<BR>
island in Erud's Crossing and the person we got jumped <BR>
by the Island Madman.  He is a spell caster and 2 <BR>
level 15's (a Paladin and Magician) were able to <BR>
defeat him.  He dropped a piece of Damask armor and<BR>
the Earring.  I have been to the island many times since <BR>
with other characters and have never seen that NPC again.<BR>
This was on Veeshan.  The magician kept the earring a<BR>
and still gets offers from other players to sell the<BR>
item and the best offer was 60pp.  Not sure why someone<BR>
would offer 60pp for this item since it appears <BR>
to only at magic resistance.  Maybe they just liked the<BR>
way it looked.<BR>
<BR>
Evince Vindicius<BR>
27th level Bard<BR>
Veeshan
