				OK - I have spent two 5 hour sessions on this island since last post.  <BR>
<BR>
I cannont tell you how utterly boring it is.  I have since taken up tailoring, mostly for my Monk only tunic in which I have to sew a NO DROP item, and partly to alleviate the boredom of killing 15 lvl mobs at 33 :(<BR>
<BR>
Last night I noticed paterns pop up as i killed things.  I am pretty convinced you have to kill the Isle Beetles and snakes to get spiders to pop.  Then kill spiders to get vampire bats. Then the sailor zombies and skeletons show up.  (I'm still totalling all cat peeps except the vendor).  You also see fire elementals pop up at the end of this heiarchy.  About every 20-40 minutes an island madman will show up, and about 1/4 of them are casters.  (As far as i can see, no such thing as an Erudite Madman, but there are casters)<BR>
<BR>
Over five hours i managed to kill 5 caster madmen.  I noticed that is a caster and a fire elemental pop simultaneously, the fire elemental will kill the caster (I of course, put this process to an end, but it WAS about to happen).<BR>
<BR>
Am I to assume that if I continue to clear the island to see my hourly caster madman, eventually i will get the earring?  <BR>
<BR>
Emil Sinclair<BR>
