				This doesn't pertain to the item so much as how to get it...I've had 5 chars lvl up at EX, and I've played at odd hours when no-one else was there...from what I observed, killing Vampire Bats spawn the madmen...I spent a couple hours testing the theory killing only bats and wisps (unles wisps have a hand in it which i doubt) and it works, but is a bit eradic...not every bat spawns a madman...but sometimes you can get 3 or 4 in a row...I don't know the reason...anyway, when i was testing this, I never saw the necro bat or an erudite madman....coincidence? Not sure, but that may be the place holder. Also, didn't find this on any of the madmen that I have killed with any of my chars.<BR>
