				<BR>
hello all. just to let you know that while riding the boat in circles through erudes crossing i decided to take my level 13 enchanter on a vacation. i bound myself to the docks at kerra isle and started killing wisps. found out quickly not to kill the beetles cause the cats rape you and not to kill the spiders even if they con blue to me because they are fond of gang rape. lost 7 bubbles of exp learning this lesson. i was killed quite unexpectantly buy a urudian madman shortly after i regained my 13th level and had to recrute a level 20 ranger to help kill it. it conned yellow to me but hit like a red con critter. i got a earring of fire resistance of him. within seconds of looting this guy a second uriden madman who conned red to me jumped my partner. it was a very close fight because he had not healed fully yet. he ended up diying and i got in the last swing to finally take this thing down. there was a damsk robe and the earring of magic reflection on him. i have camped this island for 3 real weeks on and off and only saw and island madman one other time just as i was logging off. :(  i think this is an extreamly rare pop or like previous peeps have said that killing certain things MIGHT make him come in. i no longer camp the island but spend a few hours there testing out theories whenever im in the area. i will let you know if i find out what it takes to make the erudian pop.<BR>
